WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.984
=Episode 28=

01:56.282 --> 01:57.081
I am already

01:57.081 --> 01:58.562
at the place

01:58.562 --> 01:59.601
where we first met.

02:00.042 --> 02:02.361
Batik Shop?

02:03.241 --> 02:05.002
I see it.

02:06.881 --> 02:07.842
Alright, talk later.

02:08.962 --> 02:09.761
Thanks.

02:17.641 --> 02:19.201
This pattern is absolutely stunning.

02:19.201 --> 02:20.362
See if you like any.

02:21.201 --> 02:23.002
This pouch is a linen-cotton blend.

02:23.441 --> 02:24.682
It's hand-dyed.

02:24.721 --> 02:25.562
Take one.

02:25.761 --> 02:26.362
Looks good?

02:26.522 --> 02:27.362
Sure.

02:28.921 --> 02:29.641
I'll take this.

02:29.802 --> 02:30.242
Okay.

02:32.122 --> 02:33.041
Can I see this?

02:33.122 --> 02:34.362
You have great taste.

02:34.402 --> 02:35.082
What I sell

02:35.082 --> 02:36.321
is dyed myself.

02:36.321 --> 02:37.201
Each one is unique.

02:37.201 --> 02:37.682
This color

02:37.682 --> 02:38.761
really appeals to me.

02:41.282 --> 02:41.881
Take a look.

02:42.481 --> 02:43.282
Does this look nice?

02:43.321 --> 02:44.122
Beautiful.

02:44.201 --> 02:45.122
Gorgeous.

02:45.481 --> 02:46.921
Looks perfect on you.

02:47.282 --> 02:47.802
Thank you.

02:48.002 --> 02:49.122
I'll take both then.

02:49.321 --> 02:50.201
- Okay.
- How much?

02:50.480 --> 02:51.562
I'll give you a discount.

02:51.562 --> 02:52.282
300 yuan.

02:52.562 --> 02:53.161
(Batik Shop)
Okay.

02:56.802 --> 02:57.481
Madam,

02:57.921 --> 02:58.881
you just mentioned

02:58.881 --> 03:00.921
that these are all your own creations.

03:01.562 --> 03:02.082
Sure.

03:02.562 --> 03:03.481
I dye fabrics for fun.

03:03.481 --> 03:04.041
I've paid.

03:04.721 --> 03:05.201
Got it.

03:06.161 --> 03:07.682
May I ask something?

03:07.921 --> 03:08.562
Well,

03:08.802 --> 03:11.641
to have different blues,

03:11.682 --> 03:13.362
is there a special technique?

03:16.321 --> 03:17.362
I came here

03:17.402 --> 03:18.802
to study botanical dyeing.

03:18.842 --> 03:20.441
Hope to learn from your expertise.

03:22.282 --> 03:23.562
Few young people nowadays

03:23.562 --> 03:24.761
appreciate botanical dyeing.

03:25.161 --> 03:26.201
No need for formalities.

03:26.481 --> 03:28.402
Let's exchange knowledge.

03:29.641 --> 03:30.441
You already

03:30.441 --> 03:31.682
know quite a lot.

03:31.888 --> 03:33.562
The secret of traditional indigo dyeing

03:33.562 --> 03:35.242
lies in making indigo paste.

03:36.441 --> 03:36.962
However,

03:36.962 --> 03:38.122
precise proportion and timing

03:38.122 --> 03:39.242
are crucial.

03:39.441 --> 03:40.242
For instance,

03:40.362 --> 03:41.201
plant ash proportions

03:41.441 --> 03:42.282
being off

03:42.562 --> 03:44.122
or insufficient fermentation time

03:44.161 --> 03:45.761
yields dull grayish blues.

03:47.522 --> 03:48.441
So,

03:48.481 --> 03:50.441
few achieve your level

03:50.601 --> 03:51.522
of mastery?

03:51.721 --> 03:52.481
Not like that.

03:54.362 --> 03:55.842
I visited

03:55.881 --> 03:57.962
the textile exhibition.

03:58.721 --> 04:00.362
I saw a piece made

04:00.641 --> 04:01.362
by Chu Dongfeng,

04:01.362 --> 04:03.201
the famous batik artist.

04:04.282 --> 04:05.562
Very impressive.

04:06.522 --> 04:07.562
Sadly,

04:07.881 --> 04:09.041
they say he lost inspiration

04:09.041 --> 04:10.481
from the blues in his life.

04:10.761 --> 04:11.481
So,

04:11.761 --> 04:12.881
he has stopped creating.

04:13.921 --> 04:15.921
He lives alone now,

04:16.321 --> 04:18.201
selling produce

04:18.201 --> 04:18.961
to get by.

04:19.401 --> 04:20.441
He cuts all social ties,

04:21.401 --> 04:22.521
living alone.

04:23.602 --> 04:24.362
Seems pitiable.

04:25.401 --> 04:26.602
Don't pity him.

04:27.362 --> 04:28.242
He deserves it.

04:31.162 --> 04:32.362
You know him?

04:33.002 --> 04:33.562
No.

04:33.602 --> 04:35.401
After all, Gubei Town is not big.

04:35.521 --> 04:37.281
He's just creatively bankrupt.

04:37.362 --> 04:38.602
So he made an excuse.

04:39.521 --> 04:40.441
For years,

04:40.482 --> 04:41.722
he's been merely

04:41.722 --> 04:42.722
recycling old ideas.

04:43.042 --> 04:44.362
Can't keep up with trends.

04:44.841 --> 04:46.242
What a waste of talent.

04:46.802 --> 04:48.441
He is a batik genius.

04:50.922 --> 04:52.922
The batik pattern I saw

04:52.922 --> 04:54.242
at the exhibition

04:54.562 --> 04:55.682
looks similar to the design

04:55.961 --> 04:56.482
on the pouch

04:56.482 --> 04:57.922
you made.

04:58.961 --> 04:59.881
Did you two

04:59.961 --> 05:01.242
create it together?

05:07.362 --> 05:08.722
You know about our relationship?

05:13.562 --> 05:15.722
The reason I came to see you today

05:15.722 --> 05:16.841
is to tell you

05:17.521 --> 05:18.281
that Master Chu

05:18.281 --> 05:19.722
never gave up on batik techniques.

05:20.362 --> 05:21.042
He failed

05:21.042 --> 05:22.722
to find the touch of blue in life.

05:23.922 --> 05:25.881
To put it bluntly, it's all about you...

05:25.881 --> 05:26.441
Enough.

05:28.002 --> 05:29.042
I knew it!

05:29.562 --> 05:30.521
Young people like you

05:30.562 --> 05:32.162
wouldn't love botanical dyeing.

05:33.281 --> 05:34.722
Tell him from me.

05:34.961 --> 05:36.722
Stop coveting
my indigo dyeing techniques.

05:37.162 --> 05:37.802
Mrs. Chu.

05:38.482 --> 05:39.602
I know

05:39.602 --> 05:40.641
you're still angry

05:40.802 --> 05:41.922
with him now.

05:42.401 --> 05:43.802
Why don't you two sit down

05:43.802 --> 05:44.641
and talk?

05:44.961 --> 05:45.841
Let Master Chu himself

05:45.841 --> 05:46.881
explain everything to you.

05:47.002 --> 05:48.802
Or maybe you two collaborate
one more time?

05:48.922 --> 05:49.362
I think...

05:49.362 --> 05:49.881
Collaborate?

05:50.321 --> 05:52.122
Why should I work with him?

05:52.682 --> 05:53.401
I have to go.

05:53.441 --> 05:53.961
See you.

05:55.081 --> 05:55.521
Wait.

06:01.122 --> 06:01.562
Hello?

06:01.641 --> 06:02.602
How's it going?

06:02.722 --> 06:03.362
Going well?

06:05.081 --> 06:05.761
Not well.

06:06.641 --> 06:07.482
I've sent a video

06:07.482 --> 06:08.242
to your phone.

06:08.482 --> 06:09.042
Take a look.

06:20.761 --> 06:21.602
Master Chu?

06:33.081 --> 06:33.802
Master Chu.

06:35.401 --> 06:36.002
Master Chu.

06:36.641 --> 06:37.201
Master Chu.

06:37.602 --> 06:38.242
Master Chu.

06:43.002 --> 06:43.441
Excuse me.

06:44.761 --> 06:46.602
Is that person Chu Dongfeng?

06:46.841 --> 06:47.841
I don't know him.

06:48.081 --> 06:49.002
But he comes here often

06:49.242 --> 06:50.682
with an annual membership.

06:50.841 --> 06:51.682
Every time he visits,

06:51.722 --> 06:53.162
he acts mysteriously.

06:53.562 --> 06:54.162
Super weird.

06:55.081 --> 06:55.562
Thanks.

06:59.521 --> 07:01.042
Our traditional Chinese

07:01.042 --> 07:01.961
batik techniques

07:02.562 --> 07:03.482
can be applied

07:03.482 --> 07:04.641
not only in daily life

07:04.881 --> 07:06.881
but also integrated
with various art forms.

07:06.961 --> 07:07.562
Also...

07:07.841 --> 07:08.881
Master Chu?

07:13.841 --> 07:15.242
Why did he go learn this

07:15.281 --> 07:16.722
in such a secretive way?

07:17.081 --> 07:18.242
He bought an annual pass.

07:18.562 --> 07:19.401
Annual pass?

07:23.042 --> 07:24.562
But Mrs. Chu told me

07:24.602 --> 07:26.281
that Master Chu is a stick in the mud.

07:27.441 --> 07:28.881
He clearly already started to study

07:29.482 --> 07:30.401
and has been changing.

07:30.881 --> 07:31.881
Why keep this

07:31.881 --> 07:32.602
from her?

07:34.602 --> 07:35.961
Changing oneself

07:36.042 --> 07:37.201
isn't that easy.

07:37.961 --> 07:39.362
I guess he's afraid

07:39.362 --> 07:40.802
Mrs. Chu won't believe him

07:41.242 --> 07:42.448
and thinks he's pretending.

07:45.122 --> 07:45.961
Shen Haoming.

07:47.722 --> 07:49.122
Don't tell me it's a coincidence.

07:49.122 --> 07:50.042
It truly is.

07:52.281 --> 07:53.602
Hello? Sophia.

07:54.961 --> 07:56.802
Why did you divorce Mr. Shen?

07:57.802 --> 07:58.682
He already confessed

07:58.682 --> 08:00.521
about you two being
in the cooling-off period.

08:01.682 --> 08:02.362
But my husband

08:02.362 --> 08:03.682
still decided to work with him.

08:04.201 --> 08:05.761
After all, Jinda Group is outstanding.

08:06.242 --> 08:07.362
Are you okay?

08:10.881 --> 08:11.162
Hey.

08:11.162 --> 08:11.722
Chunling.

08:11.841 --> 08:12.242
Here.

08:13.521 --> 08:14.162
Soda.

08:15.841 --> 08:16.641
Thanks, Chunling.

08:19.081 --> 08:20.482
This Chu's ex-wife's stuff?

08:21.722 --> 08:22.122
Sure.

08:22.441 --> 08:24.081
I just met Mrs. Chu.

08:24.242 --> 08:25.201
She left it here.

08:25.401 --> 08:26.401
I'll return it to her.

08:26.841 --> 08:27.562
It's a gift

08:27.562 --> 08:28.401
from Chu.

08:28.562 --> 08:29.648
She's worn it for decades.

08:31.081 --> 08:32.041
So this means a lot

08:32.041 --> 08:32.722
to her?

08:32.761 --> 08:33.442
Absolutely.

08:34.041 --> 08:34.842
You two chat.

08:38.041 --> 08:38.561
Look,

08:39.161 --> 08:39.962
Mrs. Chu

08:39.962 --> 08:41.041
never gets over Master Chu.

08:41.761 --> 08:42.722
Yet she denies it.

08:43.881 --> 08:45.322
Master Chu can recreate the color,

08:45.842 --> 08:47.401
but he insists he can't.

08:48.362 --> 08:49.602
They're both just

08:49.761 --> 08:50.921
hiding their true feelings.

08:51.122 --> 08:52.041
Why can't people

08:52.041 --> 08:53.482
face their own hearts?

08:53.921 --> 08:54.482
It's not

08:54.482 --> 08:55.442
a difficult thing to do.

09:08.242 --> 09:09.962
Since this hairpin is so important,

09:10.281 --> 09:12.482
return it to Mrs. Chu.

09:14.722 --> 09:16.002
Maybe this is fate.

09:30.761 --> 09:31.761
Why do you have it?

09:32.202 --> 09:32.801
Obviously,

09:32.801 --> 09:34.161
the owner gave it to me.

09:35.482 --> 09:36.362
She gave it to you?

09:37.442 --> 09:37.962
Why?

09:38.681 --> 09:40.242
She's waiting at the Mountaintop Cafe.

09:41.041 --> 09:42.002
She wants to see you.

09:42.122 --> 09:42.801
She gave me this

09:42.801 --> 09:43.842
in case you doubt her.

09:45.722 --> 09:46.881
I don't believe it.

09:48.041 --> 09:49.242
If she wanted to see me,

09:49.681 --> 09:50.641
she would've come.

09:51.482 --> 09:51.962
Fine.

09:52.362 --> 09:53.842
If I can't convince you,

09:54.082 --> 09:55.401
I'll just tell Mrs. Chu

09:55.722 --> 09:56.521
you're not going.

09:58.482 --> 09:59.041
Wait.

10:03.242 --> 10:03.921
Mrs. Chu.

10:06.322 --> 10:07.122
It's you?

10:08.722 --> 10:10.002
Did you

10:10.002 --> 10:11.761
lose an important hairpin?

10:12.641 --> 10:13.521
How do you know?

10:13.761 --> 10:14.442
You found it?

10:14.482 --> 10:14.881
No.

10:15.602 --> 10:16.681
Master Chu found it.

10:16.881 --> 10:17.602
He said he would

10:17.602 --> 10:19.161
wait for you at the Mountaintop Cafe.

10:20.202 --> 10:21.202
He has it?

10:22.801 --> 10:24.002
I didn't see this coming.

10:26.002 --> 10:27.082
Ms. Wang,

10:27.161 --> 10:28.401
please watch the shop for me.

10:28.881 --> 10:29.442
Okay.

10:30.401 --> 10:31.521
Thanks, Ms. Wang.

10:47.681 --> 10:48.442
Come on.

10:48.722 --> 10:49.801
Why did you take my stuff?

10:52.602 --> 10:53.161
Wait,

10:55.641 --> 10:57.281
didn't you ask me to come here?

10:58.561 --> 10:59.561
Are you kidding?

11:00.561 --> 11:02.202
You're talking nonsense!

11:02.602 --> 11:03.002
Please,

11:03.002 --> 11:04.242
stop playing dumb.

11:11.561 --> 11:13.521
Are they arguing?

11:14.602 --> 11:15.561
Probably not.

11:16.722 --> 11:17.362
Why?

11:18.161 --> 11:19.442
Look!

11:19.921 --> 11:21.442
She's already wearing the hairpin.

11:22.041 --> 11:22.561
Mrs...

11:23.322 --> 11:24.082
See?

11:25.002 --> 11:25.681
But she doesn't

11:25.722 --> 11:26.322
look happy.

11:26.322 --> 11:26.761
Liar.

11:29.602 --> 11:30.122
Weird.

11:31.401 --> 11:32.002
Master Chu!

11:32.761 --> 11:33.202
Mrs. Chu.

11:33.202 --> 11:34.401
Master! Master!

11:34.401 --> 11:34.602
Liar.

11:36.881 --> 11:37.242
Well...

11:37.242 --> 11:38.281
You liar!

11:39.002 --> 11:40.681
Yes, I tricked you.

11:41.521 --> 11:42.722
But that was a perfect chance!

11:42.722 --> 11:43.842
Why didn't you take it?

11:45.281 --> 11:47.002
I don't

11:47.362 --> 11:49.761
need your so-called chance.

11:50.161 --> 11:51.082
Master!

11:52.362 --> 11:53.722
Pride only brings suffering.

11:54.962 --> 11:56.242
If you regret the divorce,

11:56.322 --> 11:57.242
just admit it openly.

11:57.242 --> 11:58.242
Stop talking nonsense!

11:58.602 --> 12:00.242
Who said I regret it?

12:01.482 --> 12:02.681
Because I've regretted it too.

12:04.521 --> 12:06.641
I was just as arrogant as you.

12:07.561 --> 12:08.521
I lost

12:08.561 --> 12:09.681
the most important person.

12:10.521 --> 12:11.602
She gave me chances,

12:12.722 --> 12:14.202
but I couldn't swallow my pride.

12:14.962 --> 12:16.761
I refused to admit I still cared.

12:17.722 --> 12:19.002
She felt extremely disappointed.

12:19.482 --> 12:20.761
No matter what I did afterwards,

12:20.962 --> 12:22.082
she refused to believe me.

12:23.561 --> 12:24.122
And now?

12:25.322 --> 12:25.921
Master.

12:27.362 --> 12:28.641
If you want the answer,

12:29.681 --> 12:30.362
why not try it

12:30.362 --> 12:31.322
yourself?

12:33.362 --> 12:34.761
Confessing your love is nothing

12:34.801 --> 12:35.801
to be ashamed of.

12:36.881 --> 12:38.202
Don't fear her rejection.

12:38.202 --> 12:39.521
If once fails, try again.

12:40.602 --> 12:41.681
Let me be honest with you.

12:43.281 --> 12:45.322
All your talking won't change anything.

12:46.442 --> 12:48.242
She's no longer interested in me.

12:50.482 --> 12:51.161
Then why does she

12:51.161 --> 12:52.761
still wear that wedding hairpin?

12:54.442 --> 12:56.002
Isn't that clear enough?

12:56.842 --> 12:59.056
After the divorce,
why hasn't she found someone new?

12:59.681 --> 13:00.602
Stop making excuses

13:00.602 --> 13:02.161
for your own cowardice.

13:02.242 --> 13:03.824
Taking initiative is a man's thing.

13:04.322 --> 13:05.322
You've dyed many blues.

13:05.362 --> 13:06.681
Why miss the one you love?

13:07.801 --> 13:08.921
Because deep down you know

13:10.521 --> 13:11.681
you're waiting for her.

13:12.322 --> 13:13.041
Mrs. Chu.

13:13.122 --> 13:14.161
Wait.

13:14.242 --> 13:14.921
Wait.

13:15.801 --> 13:16.401
My foot...

13:18.202 --> 13:18.681
Miss.

13:19.041 --> 13:20.242
You've crossed the line.

13:20.362 --> 13:21.482
I know. I'm sorry.

13:21.681 --> 13:23.082
But I didn't mean to.

13:23.082 --> 13:23.921
I mean no harm.

13:24.122 --> 13:24.881
I just wanted

13:24.921 --> 13:25.801
to help you

13:25.801 --> 13:26.761
and Master Chu

13:26.761 --> 13:27.921
sit down and talk properly.

13:28.002 --> 13:28.401
So...

13:28.401 --> 13:29.401
Who do you think you are?

13:29.881 --> 13:30.842
None of your business!

13:31.242 --> 13:32.082
I don't need you.

13:34.401 --> 13:35.122
Mrs. Chu,

13:35.322 --> 13:36.281
I don't know

13:36.281 --> 13:37.842
what Master Chu told you earlier.

13:39.801 --> 13:41.521
But you mean everything to him.

13:41.842 --> 13:42.761
Stop kidding me.

13:43.002 --> 13:43.881
I mean everything?

13:44.561 --> 13:46.041
I know my place.

13:46.482 --> 13:48.002
He just covets my special blue.

13:49.801 --> 13:51.161
That's the misunderstanding!

13:52.962 --> 13:54.602
He could recreate the same blue.

13:55.002 --> 13:55.722
The reason

13:55.722 --> 13:56.602
he can't create now

13:56.681 --> 13:57.921
is that you left him.

13:58.921 --> 14:00.442
He's lost his inspiration.

14:02.681 --> 14:03.442
I understand.

14:06.521 --> 14:07.962
That's because

14:07.962 --> 14:09.041
I've been through

14:09.041 --> 14:10.921
the same doubts and confusion.

14:13.962 --> 14:14.561
I saw him

14:14.561 --> 14:15.722
do so much for me,

14:18.881 --> 14:20.041
yet still questioned

14:21.561 --> 14:23.561
if his love was genuine.

14:24.041 --> 14:25.202
Or does he

14:25.202 --> 14:26.401
have ulterior motives?

14:31.722 --> 14:33.002
I once wondered

14:34.801 --> 14:35.602
whether he truly

14:35.602 --> 14:36.842
cared about me

14:38.641 --> 14:39.602
or just wanted

14:39.641 --> 14:41.161
the benefits I could provide.

14:42.722 --> 14:45.281
Coming to Gubei Town

14:45.962 --> 14:47.761
and meeting you and Master Chu

14:48.041 --> 14:50.002
made me rethink love.

14:50.722 --> 14:51.761
That's why I decided

14:54.921 --> 14:56.122
to give our relationship

14:58.362 --> 14:59.401
another chance.

15:02.322 --> 15:03.442
Two people who care

15:03.442 --> 15:04.122
for each other

15:05.641 --> 15:07.122
shouldn't spend years

15:07.322 --> 15:08.122
drowning in doubt.

15:09.602 --> 15:10.482
Instead, just believe

15:12.281 --> 15:13.681
that every effort he makes

15:13.962 --> 15:14.722
is for you.

15:18.202 --> 15:18.602
Oh!

15:19.281 --> 15:20.362
Let me show you something.

15:24.401 --> 15:25.122
Look at this.

15:27.801 --> 15:28.561
Master Chu.

15:31.362 --> 15:32.801
He secretly visited the exhibition

15:33.921 --> 15:34.962
with an annual pass.

15:37.641 --> 15:38.281
See?

15:38.521 --> 15:40.002
He's been changing,

15:40.602 --> 15:41.842
just bad at communicating.

15:42.881 --> 15:44.161
Misunderstandings grew

15:44.161 --> 15:45.041
deeper and deeper.

15:45.362 --> 15:46.322
Things end up like this.

15:49.681 --> 15:51.002
We saw his courtyard

15:53.681 --> 15:55.401
filled with different blues.

15:55.921 --> 15:56.681
Well,

15:57.122 --> 15:58.362
you should also know.

15:58.921 --> 16:00.041
With his skills,

16:00.561 --> 16:01.322
he can

16:01.322 --> 16:02.801
recreate the same blue as yours.

16:04.442 --> 16:05.521
Yet he discarded

16:05.521 --> 16:06.362
the fabrics.

16:07.202 --> 16:08.881
What you really want to know is

16:10.881 --> 16:11.561
whether he

16:11.561 --> 16:13.002
desires the blue dye you created

16:15.242 --> 16:16.482
or you as a person.

16:22.041 --> 16:22.722
I don't believe.

16:23.561 --> 16:25.041
He is even afraid of admitting it.

16:25.602 --> 16:27.002
Nobody can speak for him.

16:27.442 --> 16:28.641
Who says I'm afraid?

16:37.681 --> 16:39.082
Help me dye it again.

16:46.362 --> 16:47.482
Can't you dye it yourself?

16:48.801 --> 16:49.680
You don't need me.

16:50.482 --> 16:51.801
What I want is

16:53.322 --> 16:54.561
the person who dyes the fabric.

17:10.361 --> 17:11.601
We'll soon see the new creation

17:11.642 --> 17:12.922
by Master Chu

17:12.922 --> 17:13.722
and Mrs. Chu.

17:14.162 --> 17:15.761
Old partners work best together.

17:17.682 --> 17:18.121
Look,

17:18.521 --> 17:19.521
there's a show tonight.

17:20.002 --> 17:20.642
Will you come?

17:21.361 --> 17:21.922
Of course.

17:22.521 --> 17:24.041
Good luck!

17:33.642 --> 17:35.202
Chen Shimei.

17:35.882 --> 17:37.361
You're ungrateful,

17:37.882 --> 17:39.841
plotting against your wife!

17:39.962 --> 17:40.882
Guards!

17:42.361 --> 17:43.882
(The New Opera of The Case of Chen Shimei)
Execute him!

17:44.002 --> 17:44.682
Yes!

17:50.442 --> 17:52.162
Show mercy!

17:53.561 --> 17:55.521
I admit my guilt.

17:56.202 --> 17:57.722
A guilt is a guilt.

17:58.041 --> 17:59.121
Too late for regrets.

17:59.321 --> 18:00.281
Execute him!

18:02.081 --> 18:03.361
Show mercy!

18:06.121 --> 18:06.682
Your Honor,

18:07.521 --> 18:09.402
I don't fear death.

18:10.202 --> 18:11.281
When I recall

18:11.561 --> 18:13.202
how I treated my wife,

18:13.722 --> 18:15.521
I feel deep remorse.

18:16.521 --> 18:17.682
My death matters little,

18:18.962 --> 18:20.121
and I don't

18:21.202 --> 18:22.442
deserve any forgiveness.

18:23.121 --> 18:24.081
But considering

18:24.882 --> 18:26.361
my thousand-year reincarnation,

18:27.521 --> 18:28.882
please grant me one chance

18:29.841 --> 18:31.402
to show her my reformation

18:33.242 --> 18:34.682
and accept my penance.

18:35.962 --> 18:36.962
If this is allowed,

18:37.242 --> 18:38.081
I'll die

18:38.801 --> 18:40.321
with no regrets.

18:40.722 --> 18:42.041
This

18:42.922 --> 18:44.882
sounds somewhat moving.

18:45.761 --> 18:46.402
Madam Qin,

18:47.002 --> 18:48.162
he wishes to change.

18:48.442 --> 18:49.841
What are your demands?

18:51.482 --> 18:52.361
Your Honor,

18:52.442 --> 18:54.402
a private word please.

18:57.722 --> 18:58.761
Very well.

19:00.642 --> 19:02.002
Madam Qin stated

19:02.561 --> 19:03.601
she wants no gold,

19:04.002 --> 19:05.162
no silver.

19:05.521 --> 19:07.882
She demands spiritual compensation.

19:08.402 --> 19:09.922
Three requirements

19:10.121 --> 19:12.002
must be met

19:12.922 --> 19:14.002
for your death sentence

19:14.442 --> 19:16.002
to be commuted.

19:16.882 --> 19:17.761
Material wealth

19:18.402 --> 19:19.882
can't compensate

19:21.002 --> 19:22.361
for Qin Xianglian's years

19:22.601 --> 19:24.801
of suffering during her pursuit.

19:25.402 --> 19:27.162
Whatever the cost,

19:27.922 --> 19:29.202
I'll accept it.

19:30.281 --> 19:30.922
Good.

19:31.561 --> 19:33.482
Carry a thousand dan of rice

19:34.121 --> 19:37.442
to repay her devotion.

19:40.482 --> 19:41.962
Bring rice!

19:42.242 --> 19:42.962
Yes!

19:59.081 --> 20:00.081
Is this enough?

20:00.321 --> 20:01.601
- No!
- No!

20:02.321 --> 20:03.841
More rice!

20:06.962 --> 20:07.442
Yes!

20:08.561 --> 20:09.682
Is this enough?

20:10.081 --> 20:11.202
- No!
- No!

20:11.642 --> 20:12.882
Bring more!

20:12.922 --> 20:13.722
Yes!

20:18.081 --> 20:19.162
Now enough?

20:19.361 --> 20:20.761
- No!
- No!

20:20.801 --> 20:23.002
More rice!

20:25.642 --> 20:27.081
Enough?

20:43.281 --> 20:44.202
Madam Qin,

20:44.922 --> 20:46.682
are you satisfied?

20:48.801 --> 20:50.321
Good.

20:53.002 --> 20:55.962
- Great!
- Great!

21:07.321 --> 21:08.361
I once didn't

21:08.442 --> 21:09.242
understand love.

21:11.081 --> 21:11.962
So,

21:12.162 --> 21:13.962
when seeking instant benefits,

21:15.242 --> 21:16.361
I lost someone

21:17.442 --> 21:18.682
who truly cared for me.

21:21.922 --> 21:23.121
I once swore

21:24.642 --> 21:25.722
to win her back.

21:27.202 --> 21:28.521
Yet I was arrogant.

21:28.521 --> 21:29.761
My so-called sincerity

21:31.162 --> 21:32.041
was crushed

21:33.402 --> 21:34.521
by pragmatism

21:35.281 --> 21:36.841
and calculation.

21:38.321 --> 21:39.722
Time after time,

21:40.521 --> 21:41.162
I hurt her.

21:47.521 --> 21:48.442
Thank you

21:51.561 --> 21:53.081
for giving me this opportunity

21:53.402 --> 21:54.682
to speak my mind.

21:56.922 --> 21:57.922
This made me

21:59.321 --> 22:00.801
realize my own shortcomings

22:03.121 --> 22:04.202
and clarified

22:06.962 --> 22:09.402
whether I truly loved her

22:10.962 --> 22:12.761
or merely loved being loved by her.

22:16.281 --> 22:17.682
If you ask me again

22:17.722 --> 22:18.801
what kind of person I am,

22:20.281 --> 22:21.162
I'll tell you

22:23.162 --> 22:24.882
I'm the one who discovered

22:26.121 --> 22:27.521
I still love you.

22:54.202 --> 22:54.761
Good.

22:55.682 --> 22:58.442
- Great!
- Great!

