â™ªThen I'm pleasedâ™ª

23:53.442 --> 23:53.922
Ms. Qiao.

23:54.002 --> 23:55.561
The offline experience store

23:55.561 --> 23:57.162
is progressing smoother than expected.

23:57.402 --> 23:58.801
Lease contracts for three stores

23:58.801 --> 23:59.561
have been signed.

23:59.601 --> 24:01.162
Interior design plans are finalized.

24:01.162 --> 24:01.722
Next steps

24:01.722 --> 24:03.081
involve payments for rent,

24:03.162 --> 24:04.081
renovation,

24:04.202 --> 24:05.561
and materials.

24:06.121 --> 24:06.682
Good.

24:07.402 --> 24:08.722
Hopefully, before Ms. Xu returns,

24:08.722 --> 24:10.601
we'll finalize
offline operations properly.

24:10.601 --> 24:12.361
Then promptly report to Yuanhang Capital

24:12.642 --> 24:13.922
about our project status.

24:14.482 --> 24:15.041
Understood.

24:15.242 --> 24:17.041
The contract requires transferring

24:17.041 --> 24:18.761
one year's rent within two weeks.

24:19.561 --> 24:20.601
Verify the amounts

24:20.601 --> 24:21.922
and details with Mr. Lin first.

24:22.224 --> 24:24.041
After my confirmation,
proceed with payment.

24:24.402 --> 24:25.081
Got it.

24:25.521 --> 24:26.202
Ms. Qiao.

24:26.722 --> 24:28.041
Can we slow down

24:28.041 --> 24:29.482
the experience store progress?

24:30.361 --> 24:30.962
Why?

24:31.041 --> 24:32.801
I suggest reallocating offline funds

24:32.841 --> 24:33.801
to production.

24:34.162 --> 24:36.402
If we delay supplier payments,

24:36.601 --> 24:38.162
we can't afford the penalty fees.

24:39.202 --> 24:40.561
Wasn't the bank loan

24:40.561 --> 24:42.002
supposed to be approved this week?

24:42.121 --> 24:43.361
Originally, yes,

24:43.561 --> 24:44.962
but the bank suddenly notified me

24:44.962 --> 24:46.121
of tightened policies.

24:46.281 --> 24:47.922
All non-compliant loans

24:47.922 --> 24:49.002
got rejected.

24:51.841 --> 24:53.321
Keep proceeding as planned.

24:53.482 --> 24:55.121
I'll discuss whether to slow down

24:55.521 --> 24:57.162
with Mr. Lin.

24:57.521 --> 24:58.642
Don't worry.

24:58.962 --> 25:00.202
Just focus on your work,

25:00.202 --> 25:00.882
okay?

25:01.722 --> 25:02.202
Okay.

25:03.682 --> 25:04.962
I think I should visit the bank.

25:04.962 --> 25:06.162
Wait, I've tried already.

25:06.361 --> 25:07.281
I've done my best,

25:07.281 --> 25:08.281
but failed.

25:08.402 --> 25:09.162
That's why I came

25:09.162 --> 25:10.162
to discuss alternatives.

25:11.162 --> 25:12.642
But I previously stated

25:12.761 --> 25:14.081
the offline stores' funding

25:14.121 --> 25:15.722
comes from Yuanhang.

25:17.321 --> 25:18.521
The money is regulated.

25:18.521 --> 25:20.002
Redirecting it violates agreements.

25:21.922 --> 25:23.281
Then securing loans

25:23.321 --> 25:24.281
remains our only option.

25:25.002 --> 25:25.442
No worries.

25:25.561 --> 25:26.482
I'll try other banks

25:26.642 --> 25:28.081
one by one.

25:28.281 --> 25:28.962
Don't worry.

25:28.962 --> 25:30.521
Let's work separately. I'll make calls.

25:37.321 --> 25:37.841
Yan.

25:38.402 --> 25:39.962
Still at work?

25:40.321 --> 25:41.601
I'm handling something.

25:42.722 --> 25:43.642
Anything happened?

25:44.521 --> 25:45.281
Nothing serious.

25:45.402 --> 25:46.081
We'll handle it.

25:46.962 --> 25:48.281
How are things with Shen Haoming?

25:48.281 --> 25:50.162
It's been ages
since I heard you vent about him.

25:50.162 --> 25:52.561
I'll talk about it when I get back.

25:53.722 --> 25:54.841
Guess what?

25:54.841 --> 25:56.400
There is a hope for being authorized.

25:56.482 --> 25:57.761
I'll stay here a few more days.

25:57.882 --> 25:58.482
Good.

25:58.561 --> 25:59.801
Stay there without worries.

25:59.882 --> 26:01.002
It's all under control.

26:01.002 --> 26:02.482
You get along with Shen Haoming.

26:02.601 --> 26:03.202
Don't worry.

26:03.962 --> 26:05.202
Alright, I'll hang up now.

26:05.682 --> 26:06.162
Bye.

26:11.722 --> 26:13.041
I'll keep working on it tomorrow.

26:14.162 --> 26:15.561
You should get back early.

26:49.041 --> 26:49.761
Honestly,

26:51.521 --> 26:52.162
I've never seen

26:52.162 --> 26:53.442
an outstanding woman like you

26:54.321 --> 26:54.841
obsessing

26:54.841 --> 26:55.922
over one man for years.

27:01.242 --> 27:02.321
But he doesn't care.

27:06.962 --> 27:07.962
The more devoted I am,

27:08.242 --> 27:09.402
the more I look like a fool.

27:11.202 --> 27:12.482
But strangely,

27:14.242 --> 27:15.882
despite all the rumors,

27:16.841 --> 27:18.992
there's no official news
about Shen Haoming and Xu Yan

27:19.321 --> 27:20.402
finalizing their divorce.

27:22.601 --> 27:24.202
Are they still together?

27:26.402 --> 27:27.281
You often see him.

27:27.281 --> 27:28.002
Don't you know?

27:28.442 --> 27:29.402
How would I know?

27:33.601 --> 27:34.121
Fine.

27:35.242 --> 27:36.242
Let's not talk about it.

27:36.841 --> 27:37.682
Tell me about how you

27:38.601 --> 27:39.281
and Shen Haoming

27:39.281 --> 27:40.002
first met.

27:41.041 --> 27:42.242
Back then,

27:42.922 --> 27:43.642
he and my sister

27:43.642 --> 27:45.402
attended the same university in London.

27:46.642 --> 27:47.402
Well,

27:48.521 --> 27:49.281
I was

27:49.281 --> 27:51.561
at a boarding school
taking prep courses.

27:52.442 --> 27:53.361
Later,

27:54.281 --> 27:55.162
I watched them

27:55.202 --> 27:56.682
date for a while.

27:58.962 --> 27:59.922
Afterwards,

28:00.162 --> 28:01.962
my sister broke up with him.

28:03.482 --> 28:04.442
Then later,

28:05.162 --> 28:07.281
my sister discovered she was pregnant.

28:09.361 --> 28:10.121
Pregnant?

28:11.281 --> 28:12.242
Whose child was it?

28:30.321 --> 28:32.121
What's wrong with Han Weiping?

28:33.361 --> 28:34.642
Can't even handle simple things.

28:37.002 --> 28:39.962
Baraikin chose to partner with Jinda.

28:43.242 --> 28:44.601
He couldn't find evidence

28:44.922 --> 28:46.321
of Shen Haoming and Xu Yan

28:46.321 --> 28:47.002
getting divorced.

28:48.081 --> 28:49.561
Shen Haoming performed too well

28:49.722 --> 28:50.722
in front of Baraikin.

28:54.601 --> 28:55.561
Shen Haoming and Xu Yan

28:55.561 --> 28:56.761
are nearly reconciled,

28:57.402 --> 28:59.002
yet he's still fixated on their divorce.

29:00.281 --> 29:01.121
I feel disappointed.

29:02.722 --> 29:03.601
What a fool he is!

29:05.882 --> 29:06.841
Where is Han Weiping?

29:08.962 --> 29:09.801
He will arrive soon.

29:19.761 --> 29:20.361
Dad.

29:21.402 --> 29:22.281
Nice shot.

29:24.482 --> 29:26.482
Any updates on Shen Haoming?

29:29.081 --> 29:29.601
Dad.

29:30.442 --> 29:31.962
I'm still...

29:50.682 --> 29:51.242
Mr. Lin.

29:53.281 --> 29:53.882
It's settled.

29:54.321 --> 29:55.242
Finally sorted it out.

29:56.002 --> 29:56.801
About the loan?

29:57.682 --> 29:59.202
(Feng Zhiyuan's business card)
This is my old colleague.

29:59.202 --> 30:00.361
Do you remember Feng?

30:00.482 --> 30:01.962
He's now at a bank

30:02.002 --> 30:03.561
as a senior credit specialist.

30:03.882 --> 30:05.081
I called him yesterday

30:05.162 --> 30:06.281
to inquire if his bank

30:06.281 --> 30:07.722
handles cross-regional loans.

30:07.922 --> 30:09.361
Turns out he's willing to help.

30:10.601 --> 30:11.442
That's great.

30:11.482 --> 30:12.841
So I'm checking with you.

30:13.642 --> 30:14.761
I'm fine with it.

30:14.761 --> 30:16.081
If possible, make it quick.

30:16.361 --> 30:16.841
Alright.

30:17.162 --> 30:18.361
Now I have a clear plan.

30:18.642 --> 30:19.442
But he wants us

30:19.442 --> 30:21.202
to prepare the financial statements,

30:21.202 --> 30:22.281
along with other documents.

30:22.601 --> 30:23.962
If approved smoothly, funds can

30:23.962 --> 30:25.041
be released this month.

30:25.242 --> 30:26.281
But we need to act fast.

30:26.361 --> 30:27.922
The submission window is closing soon.

30:28.242 --> 30:29.442
Alright, you get

30:29.442 --> 30:30.281
all the papers ready.

30:31.642 --> 30:32.361
All done.

30:32.482 --> 30:32.962
Take a look.

30:33.081 --> 30:34.512
Stamp it if there are no issues.

30:35.521 --> 30:36.361
Well done.

30:36.922 --> 30:37.801
Impressive.

30:39.290 --> 30:41.808
(Balance Sheet)

30:45.962 --> 30:46.761
Just stamp it here.

30:48.521 --> 30:49.361
Okay, got it.

30:49.882 --> 30:51.121
If there are no problems,

30:51.121 --> 30:51.882
after this,

30:51.922 --> 30:54.202
we'll go back home tomorrow
by high-speed rail.

30:54.561 --> 30:56.432
We'll urge him
to settle this matter quickly.

30:56.841 --> 30:58.041
Since you're the deputy,

30:58.281 --> 31:00.321
you must be present in person to sign.

31:00.801 --> 31:01.922
Let's leave early then.

31:02.482 --> 31:03.408
Early in the morning.

31:03.482 --> 31:03.962
Okay.

31:04.081 --> 31:04.882
I'll buy tickets.

31:06.361 --> 31:07.841
If this gets done successfully,

31:08.242 --> 31:08.601
I will

31:08.601 --> 31:09.521
owe you big.

31:09.962 --> 31:10.402
You don't

31:10.402 --> 31:11.242
have to thank me.

31:11.361 --> 31:13.264
Helping the company
means helping myself too.

31:14.842 --> 31:16.816
(Income Statement)

31:27.361 --> 31:28.081
Morning, Mr. Shen.

31:28.642 --> 31:29.081
Morning.

31:29.402 --> 31:30.121
Morning, Mr. Shen.

31:31.482 --> 31:31.962
Morning.

31:33.841 --> 31:34.361
Morning.

31:34.361 --> 31:34.801
Mr. Shen.

31:34.801 --> 31:35.361
Morning.

31:35.962 --> 31:37.081
Nice hairstyle.

31:38.682 --> 31:39.402
Morning, Mr. Shen.

31:40.121 --> 31:40.801
Morning.

31:40.880 --> 31:44.784
(Open Mindedness)

31:49.882 --> 31:50.801
Watch your step.

31:55.402 --> 31:56.081
Have a seat.

31:59.242 --> 31:59.761
Chairman,

31:59.761 --> 32:01.121
I'm here to report

32:01.442 --> 32:03.162
on our collaboration with Mr. Baraikin.

32:03.162 --> 32:04.722
The agreement has been signed.

32:05.162 --> 32:06.002
Early next month,

32:06.121 --> 32:07.521
our core team

32:07.642 --> 32:08.601
will fly to Moscow

32:09.081 --> 32:09.682
to handle

32:09.922 --> 32:11.242
the design aspects

32:11.482 --> 32:12.761
and operational procedures.

32:14.402 --> 32:15.242
Sit down.

32:16.361 --> 32:17.442
Regarding this project,

32:17.801 --> 32:18.361
both parties

32:18.521 --> 32:19.922
have high expectations.

32:21.402 --> 32:21.841
We aim

32:21.841 --> 32:23.321
to develop it

32:23.642 --> 32:25.801
into a landmark Jinda builds overseas.

32:27.002 --> 32:28.081
That's my objective too.

32:29.002 --> 32:30.121
All workflows

32:30.361 --> 32:30.962
and key aspects

32:31.081 --> 32:32.002
will be supervised.

32:33.162 --> 32:33.642
Moreover,

32:39.202 --> 32:40.841
according to East China's report,

32:41.018 --> 32:42.121
(Jinda: North Waichuan
Development Proposal)

32:42.121 --> 32:45.081
the North Waichuan,
adjacent to the Huanghu River,

32:46.281 --> 32:48.482
marks the first residential land release
in three years

32:48.801 --> 32:50.202
by the local government.

32:51.521 --> 32:53.561
The starting land price per square meter

32:53.922 --> 32:55.561
sets a new record.

32:56.482 --> 32:57.162
This is

32:57.162 --> 32:58.242
the biggest land auction

32:58.642 --> 33:00.682
in East China at present.

33:01.682 --> 33:02.722
You want this plot?

33:03.882 --> 33:04.321
Yes.

33:05.482 --> 33:06.321
For this land,

33:06.361 --> 33:08.841
we don't need to hold 15 percent

33:08.882 --> 33:09.722
of rental housing.

33:10.722 --> 33:12.162
Under current regulations,

33:12.202 --> 33:12.841
this increases

33:13.202 --> 33:14.882
the saleable area percentage

33:15.281 --> 33:16.081
and reduces

33:16.121 --> 33:17.281
per-unit development costs.

33:18.162 --> 33:20.281
Market expectations

33:20.361 --> 33:20.922
predict

33:21.321 --> 33:21.922
at least

33:22.002 --> 33:23.321
a 20 percent premium.

33:24.402 --> 33:25.002
Therefore,

33:25.002 --> 33:26.162
from all perspectives,

33:26.761 --> 33:27.722
this is undoubtedly

33:27.722 --> 33:29.242
the most sought-after plot

33:29.761 --> 33:30.242
and

33:30.442 --> 33:31.922
a prime development zone.

33:34.361 --> 33:35.801
I support your bid plan.

33:36.442 --> 33:37.081
You've secured

33:37.081 --> 33:38.002
a deal with Baraikin.

33:38.081 --> 33:38.642
If you also

33:39.162 --> 33:40.521
obtain the plot

33:40.601 --> 33:41.482
in North Waichuan,

33:41.922 --> 33:43.242
it will show that you,

33:44.002 --> 33:44.601
in Jinda,

33:44.801 --> 33:46.242
have sufficient credibility.

33:47.922 --> 33:48.682
Thank you.

33:49.922 --> 33:50.361
Good.

33:50.992 --> 33:52.841
There'll be a meeting
next Friday at 9:00 AM.

33:52.841 --> 33:53.482
Don't be late.

33:54.081 --> 33:55.442
The agenda is...

33:57.521 --> 33:59.361
I'll fulfill my promise to you

34:00.081 --> 34:01.361
by giving you a board seat

34:01.402 --> 34:03.041
because you made a deal with Baraikin.

34:05.002 --> 34:07.002
I should thank Mr. Baraikin

34:07.482 --> 34:09.081
for overlooking my previous concealment.

34:09.442 --> 34:10.482
I feel sorry.

34:10.842 --> 34:11.402
Haoming.

34:12.241 --> 34:13.802
Your capabilities are

34:14.161 --> 34:15.482
unquestionable.

34:16.161 --> 34:17.482
But your methods

34:19.201 --> 34:20.521
don't align with my principles.

34:23.121 --> 34:23.802
In business,

34:24.762 --> 34:26.241
integrity is fundamental.

34:27.482 --> 34:28.762
The core principle should

34:29.041 --> 34:31.322
be mutually beneficial cooperation.

34:33.241 --> 34:34.442
I don't know

34:34.442 --> 34:35.241
what caused

34:36.002 --> 34:37.402
your drastic change.

34:37.442 --> 34:38.362
But I believe

34:38.601 --> 34:39.201
you

34:39.201 --> 34:40.482
understand this deep down now.

34:41.282 --> 34:42.842
Just like the marriage

34:42.882 --> 34:43.882
between me and Yan.

34:45.442 --> 34:46.681
Our marriage

34:46.721 --> 34:47.882
was filled with arguments

34:48.121 --> 34:49.081
and deceptions.

34:50.442 --> 34:51.762
What kept us together was

34:52.681 --> 34:53.601
our sincerity.

34:55.561 --> 34:55.922
Dad.

34:56.802 --> 34:57.922
Yan and I have reconciled.

34:58.882 --> 34:59.721
I'm glad

35:01.041 --> 35:02.201
we're still married.

35:04.282 --> 35:05.601
Your mom and I

35:07.002 --> 35:08.842
are happy for you.

35:10.081 --> 35:10.882
Most importantly,

35:10.922 --> 35:12.601
Haochen will be thrilled.

35:13.201 --> 35:13.802
Yes.

35:16.802 --> 35:17.721
If you'll excuse me,

35:17.762 --> 35:18.561
I have to go.

35:23.002 --> 35:23.561
Wait.

35:32.081 --> 35:33.322
What kind of flower is this?

35:35.962 --> 35:36.681
You know,

35:37.721 --> 35:38.882
it's quite interesting.

35:39.561 --> 35:40.402
Ms. Xu,

35:41.282 --> 35:41.882
welcome back.

35:42.882 --> 35:43.561
Mr. Liang.

35:46.561 --> 35:47.482
Flowers for me?

35:48.201 --> 35:48.482
Sure.

35:48.521 --> 35:48.922
Thank you.

35:48.962 --> 35:49.521
For you.

35:50.681 --> 35:51.376
I'll put it here.

35:52.362 --> 35:53.121
Beautiful.

35:58.922 --> 36:00.601
What did you learn

36:00.762 --> 36:01.641
in Gubei Town?

36:03.362 --> 36:05.121
From theory to practice,

36:06.721 --> 36:07.201
I studied

36:07.241 --> 36:08.802
the history of botanical dyeing

36:08.842 --> 36:10.882
and learned traditional craftsmanship.

36:10.882 --> 36:11.681
It was enriching.

36:12.041 --> 36:13.041
I plan

36:13.041 --> 36:14.081
to launch a collection

36:14.081 --> 36:15.882
about botanical dyeing this autumn,

36:16.362 --> 36:17.482
which will also promote

36:17.482 --> 36:18.641
Gubei Town's heritage.

36:24.882 --> 36:25.362
Excellent.

36:26.962 --> 36:28.482
You seem to be glowing today.

36:29.762 --> 36:31.161
The romantic aura is around you.

36:35.922 --> 36:37.282
Shen Haoming and I made up.

36:39.081 --> 36:39.762
I noticed.

36:40.521 --> 36:42.201
After wrapping up current projects,

36:43.521 --> 36:45.681
I'll move back home.

36:49.282 --> 36:49.842
I understand.

36:50.962 --> 36:52.041
After making decisions,

36:52.561 --> 36:53.681
you won't change your mind.

36:55.282 --> 36:56.322
You know exactly

36:56.322 --> 36:57.081
what you want.

36:58.002 --> 36:59.121
But I still wonder

37:00.241 --> 37:00.842
why.

37:04.762 --> 37:05.601
What

37:05.601 --> 37:07.482
sustains a marriage?

37:07.721 --> 37:08.842
Either

37:09.641 --> 37:10.882
genuine mutual affection,

37:11.482 --> 37:12.442
or

37:13.601 --> 37:14.762
strategic interdependence

37:15.081 --> 37:16.002
and indivisibility.

37:17.264 --> 37:18.081
Where do you stand?

37:18.081 --> 37:18.561
Both.

37:22.922 --> 37:24.442
We used to hide things,

37:26.282 --> 37:27.561
but now we are

37:28.802 --> 37:29.641
open and honest.

37:32.762 --> 37:33.241
Thank you

37:33.241 --> 37:34.241
for telling me candidly.

37:37.121 --> 37:38.241
If your relationship status

37:38.241 --> 37:39.282
ever changes,

37:39.282 --> 37:40.041
please inform me.

37:40.041 --> 37:41.200
I can be your backup option.

37:45.081 --> 37:46.241
Actually, Shen Haoming

37:46.241 --> 37:47.521
has always been my only choice.

37:51.002 --> 37:51.882
Looks like tonight

37:51.882 --> 37:53.081
I'll need to drown my sorrows.

37:55.362 --> 37:56.681
Though you never even gave me

37:56.681 --> 37:57.601
a chance to start,

37:58.882 --> 38:00.362
I've invested so much emotionally.

38:03.002 --> 38:03.762
I need time

38:03.762 --> 38:04.482
to heal.

38:06.121 --> 38:07.322
If you can still joke around,

38:07.322 --> 38:08.282
it means you're okay.

38:08.922 --> 38:10.201
Plus, your act was convincing.

38:12.482 --> 38:13.081
Xu Yan.

38:14.601 --> 38:15.241
I'm serious.

38:16.201 --> 38:17.002
Qiao Lin,

38:17.282 --> 38:18.121
Yao, Guan, and I

38:18.521 --> 38:19.161
are all the same

38:21.241 --> 38:22.482
as your strong backers

38:22.521 --> 38:23.121
and allies.

38:24.641 --> 38:25.681
You can rely on us.

38:29.641 --> 38:30.362
I understand.

38:32.681 --> 38:33.442
Thank you.

38:34.882 --> 38:36.482
I wanted to try dating an older woman,

38:36.482 --> 38:37.641
but failed.

38:40.482 --> 38:41.802
So, we'll just be friends.

38:44.442 --> 38:45.201
May you be happy.

38:47.641 --> 38:49.842
May you always stay carefree.

38:50.721 --> 38:51.842
Sure, I will.

39:30.402 --> 39:30.962
Your godfather

39:31.002 --> 39:32.121
told me to talk with you.

39:33.121 --> 39:33.681
What's up?

39:34.521 --> 39:35.362
Shen Jinsong decided

39:35.402 --> 39:36.944
to give Shen Haoming a board seat.

39:37.081 --> 39:37.802
He's informed

39:37.802 --> 39:38.762
all shareholders.

39:39.641 --> 39:40.601
Your godfather wants us

39:40.601 --> 39:41.161
to stop this

39:41.161 --> 39:42.002
at all costs.

39:42.922 --> 39:44.482
Is Shen Haoming that easy to handle?

39:45.681 --> 39:46.962
He is at a vital time

39:47.041 --> 39:48.282
for sitting on the board.

39:48.721 --> 39:49.842
He'll be extra cautious.

39:51.121 --> 39:52.442
Plus, he's made up with Xu Yan.

39:52.762 --> 39:53.362
Now, he is

39:53.362 --> 39:54.561
riding high on success.

39:55.081 --> 39:55.842
They've reconciled?

39:56.402 --> 39:57.201
How did you know?

39:57.521 --> 39:58.962
Chen Lin is making arrangements.

40:00.002 --> 40:01.201
Xu Yan might soon

40:01.201 --> 40:02.161
move back home.

40:03.882 --> 40:05.442
I didn't see this coming.

40:05.962 --> 40:07.521
Even his love life's going smoothly?

40:07.922 --> 40:09.041
But when Fang Lei was drunk,

40:09.041 --> 40:10.002
she told me

40:10.641 --> 40:11.482
that her sister

40:11.482 --> 40:12.641
dated Shen Haoming

40:13.241 --> 40:14.161
and even got pregnant.

40:14.962 --> 40:15.802
Pregnant?

40:18.362 --> 40:19.280
What about the child?

40:19.721 --> 40:20.521
Was it born?

40:20.922 --> 40:21.802
Was it Shen Haoming's?

40:22.002 --> 40:23.201
I don't know. She didn't say.

40:23.762 --> 40:25.121
You've been with Fang Lei.

40:25.641 --> 40:27.041
Couldn't you get more information?

40:28.641 --> 40:29.241
No.

40:29.402 --> 40:30.201
She's tight-lipped.

40:30.521 --> 40:31.641
Then dig deeper.

40:32.521 --> 40:33.962
There's definitely something there.

40:42.081 --> 40:42.521
There is

40:42.521 --> 40:43.521
no surprise at all?

40:44.882 --> 40:45.442
What's wrong?

40:46.201 --> 40:47.402
Have you stopped pretending?

40:53.241 --> 40:53.601
What?

40:53.842 --> 40:54.842
How did you get hurt?

40:56.161 --> 40:56.922
At boxing class.

40:56.922 --> 40:57.762
Overdid the strength.

40:57.762 --> 40:58.282
Fracture.

40:58.322 --> 40:58.842
It's fine.

40:59.922 --> 41:01.201
How could you be so careless?

41:05.041 --> 41:06.681
Be more careful next time you box.

41:06.962 --> 41:07.882
If you're injured,

41:08.962 --> 41:10.041
who will cook for me?

41:13.442 --> 41:14.002
By the way,

41:14.402 --> 41:15.641
I saw a nice custom tailor shop

41:15.681 --> 41:17.081
while shopping today.

41:17.442 --> 41:18.241
It's pretty good.

41:18.681 --> 41:19.721
Take you there tomorrow

41:20.842 --> 41:21.962
and pick you some.

41:22.962 --> 41:24.201
Tailored suits

41:24.362 --> 41:25.842
are better than ready-to-wear.

41:29.681 --> 41:30.864
Need to tell you something.

41:31.721 --> 41:32.641
Get ready for this.

41:33.802 --> 41:34.282
Go ahead.

41:34.962 --> 41:36.282
I just received the news.

41:37.241 --> 41:38.768
Shen Haoming and Xu Yan have made up.

41:38.882 --> 41:39.882
They won't divorce.

41:53.721 --> 41:54.521
Don't be afraid.

41:55.322 --> 41:56.402
I'll always be with you.

41:58.002 --> 41:59.282
If you want to deal with him,

42:00.201 --> 42:01.002
I'll unconditionally

42:01.002 --> 42:01.762
stand on your side.

42:03.882 --> 42:04.601
I've said it.

42:06.521 --> 42:07.641
I don't care.

42:09.842 --> 42:11.081
He had a quarrel with Xu Yan,

42:11.362 --> 42:12.681
yet he chose Xu Yan in the end.

42:13.282 --> 42:14.601
He never cares about you at all.

42:15.721 --> 42:16.322
Why should he

42:16.322 --> 42:17.041
care about me?

42:17.842 --> 42:19.601
He must have his reasons

42:19.962 --> 42:20.922
to choose Xu Yan.

42:21.521 --> 42:22.640
I don't want to dig deeper.

42:23.282 --> 42:24.442
You've loved him for years.

42:25.201 --> 42:26.041
You love him,

42:26.681 --> 42:27.721
yet he hurt you.

42:28.161 --> 42:29.041
Are you letting it go?

42:38.442 --> 42:39.322
Since Shen Haoming

42:39.322 --> 42:40.241
never likes me,

42:42.081 --> 42:43.121
I should get over him.

42:50.482 --> 42:51.402
When we drank, you said

42:51.442 --> 42:52.482
your sister got pregnant

42:53.201 --> 42:53.922
in the UK.

42:56.282 --> 42:56.762
Is that

42:56.762 --> 42:57.882
Shen Haoming's child?

42:59.842 --> 43:00.802
Of course not.

43:01.201 --> 43:01.922
You misheard.

43:03.762 --> 43:04.681
How could I mishear?

43:04.681 --> 43:05.362
We were here...

43:05.362 --> 43:06.802
You drank too, didn't you?

43:07.482 --> 43:08.362
You got drunk.

43:25.802 --> 43:26.681
You guys chat.

43:27.041 --> 43:28.080
The food's almost ready.

43:29.241 --> 43:29.681
Yan.

43:29.762 --> 43:30.721
You've forgiven Haoming?

43:30.842 --> 43:31.802
You two made up?

43:35.121 --> 43:36.601
We've always been good.

43:38.521 --> 43:39.442
Come on.

43:39.482 --> 43:40.322
I have

43:40.322 --> 43:41.681
your gloomy-faced photos.

43:42.002 --> 43:43.002
Enough, just eat.

43:43.322 --> 43:43.842
Stop eating.

43:43.962 --> 43:44.882
Dinner's almost ready.

43:47.161 --> 43:47.641
Oh right,

43:48.601 --> 43:49.601
I have a gift for you.

43:49.681 --> 43:50.081
Look.

43:53.041 --> 43:53.802
What kind of gift?

43:54.041 --> 43:54.601
Have a look.

43:56.442 --> 43:57.121
More drawings.

43:57.922 --> 43:58.442
Let me see.

43:58.721 --> 43:59.282
Let me guess.

43:59.282 --> 44:00.802
You drew...

44:02.121 --> 44:03.322
These are two horns?

44:03.922 --> 44:05.842
Horns? These are tornadoes!

44:08.521 --> 44:09.002
Look,

44:09.201 --> 44:09.962
after you left,

44:09.962 --> 44:11.201
a tornado

44:11.442 --> 44:12.681
swept through our home,

44:12.681 --> 44:14.081
shattering everything.

44:14.121 --> 44:14.962
It's not complete.

44:19.282 --> 44:19.802
Look.

44:21.681 --> 44:22.402
I think this one

44:22.402 --> 44:23.362
is my best work.

44:26.322 --> 44:27.002
Turning the page?

44:31.041 --> 44:31.402
Look,

44:32.041 --> 44:32.521
this

44:32.721 --> 44:34.521
big, chubby one is my brother,

44:34.962 --> 44:35.721
and this is me.

44:36.681 --> 44:37.721
After you left,

44:38.201 --> 44:38.762
both of us

44:38.762 --> 44:40.482
desperately wanted you back.

44:40.802 --> 44:42.002
We were sad every day.

44:50.762 --> 44:51.721
And this is...

44:51.962 --> 44:52.362
You.

44:53.282 --> 44:53.842
Me?

44:54.561 --> 44:55.121
Why?

44:55.842 --> 44:56.362
See,

44:56.882 --> 44:58.601
you ventured out alone.

44:58.681 --> 44:59.762
It must've been tough.

45:00.322 --> 45:02.201
Look, you're surrounded by glaciers.

45:07.161 --> 45:07.842
Next page.

45:09.882 --> 45:10.362
Look.

45:11.561 --> 45:12.482
See,

45:12.641 --> 45:13.442
I've always

45:13.442 --> 45:14.482
kept a light on for you

45:14.641 --> 45:16.081
to guide you home.

45:19.882 --> 45:20.402
See?

45:20.442 --> 45:21.681
Now, you've returned.

45:24.161 --> 45:25.362
There are even stars here.

45:37.561 --> 45:38.681
Finally, you came back.

45:39.081 --> 45:40.201
(My Family)
We are

45:40.241 --> 45:41.002
the happiest family

45:41.002 --> 45:42.081
in the world.

45:46.362 --> 45:47.121
More after this?

45:47.561 --> 45:48.762
No. I'll draw more later.

45:50.201 --> 45:51.161
Keep drawing.

45:51.521 --> 45:52.681
Fill this entire sketchbook.

45:53.641 --> 45:54.882
To find out what happens next,

45:54.922 --> 45:56.121
stay tuned.

45:57.762 --> 45:58.322
Haochen.

45:58.601 --> 45:59.882
This is the best gift

45:59.882 --> 46:01.241
I've ever received.

46:01.561 --> 46:02.002
Really?

46:02.161 --> 46:02.641
Sure.

46:04.121 --> 46:05.648
Much better than your brother's gift.

46:05.882 --> 46:06.762
Dinner's ready.

46:07.201 --> 46:07.762
Come and eat.

46:09.081 --> 46:09.561
Come here.

46:11.322 --> 46:11.882
Haoming.

46:12.201 --> 46:12.641
Can I sleep

46:12.641 --> 46:14.201
with you two tonight?

46:14.322 --> 46:15.121
It's been ages

46:15.121 --> 46:16.482
since I slept with you two.

46:16.762 --> 46:17.601
No problem.

46:18.561 --> 46:19.121
Really?

46:19.842 --> 46:20.681
Awesome!

46:21.362 --> 46:22.681
Come and eat.

46:23.121 --> 46:24.041
What are you holding?

46:24.842 --> 46:25.482
What's this?

46:26.521 --> 46:27.402
Give it to me!

46:29.282 --> 46:29.681
Haoming.

46:29.681 --> 46:30.641
What did you cook?

46:30.882 --> 46:32.121
(My Family)
Delicious.

46:33.201 --> 46:34.096
Washed your hands?

46:34.521 --> 46:35.081
Wash.

46:38.521 --> 46:39.641
Hurry!

46:44.521 --> 46:45.922
Alright, come eat now.

46:46.641 --> 46:47.201
Yan.

46:47.282 --> 46:48.002
Yan, come on!

46:48.402 --> 46:48.922
Coming.

46:50.882 --> 46:51.802
Do you want to see?

46:52.362 --> 46:52.681
Sure.

46:52.681 --> 46:53.041
Haochen.

46:53.041 --> 46:54.282
Can I show this to him?

46:54.362 --> 46:55.482
Of course!

46:55.842 --> 46:57.121
But I already showed him.

46:59.842 --> 47:00.561
Give it to me.

47:04.121 --> 47:04.962
Eat more.

47:06.002 --> 47:06.842
Let's eat.

47:09.681 --> 47:10.721
Have some more.

47:11.041 --> 47:12.081
You eat vegetables.

47:12.721 --> 47:13.081
Here.

47:13.762 --> 47:14.322
You try this.

47:14.482 --> 47:15.241
Eat more veggies.

47:16.161 --> 47:16.802
You too.

47:17.121 --> 47:18.002
Have more vegetables.

47:26.201 --> 47:26.842
I made the bed.

47:26.882 --> 47:27.962
I'm sleeping in the middle.

47:30.201 --> 47:32.362
I want the middle spot tonight.

47:36.041 --> 47:37.002
I'll get Yan.

49:28.282 --> 49:29.041
Exactly.

49:29.442 --> 49:30.882
Dig up everything

49:31.241 --> 49:32.721
on Shen Haoming

49:32.721 --> 49:33.681
and Fang Yu

49:34.041 --> 49:35.201
studying abroad together.

49:36.201 --> 49:37.041
Key focus:

49:37.681 --> 49:38.402
the child.

49:47.834 --> 49:48.880
(Browsing History)

49:53.306 --> 49:57.136
(Saved Addresses)

49:58.874 --> 50:00.790
â™ªLike fireworks that lovedâ™ª

50:00.790 --> 50:02.449
â™ªRushing toward the starsâ™ª

50:02.449 --> 50:04.508
â™ªUndaunted by painâ™ª

50:05.351 --> 50:07.252
â™ªFearless of flamesâ™ª

50:07.252 --> 50:10.906
â™ªEven if just a fleeting sparkleâ™ª

50:11.911 --> 50:13.735
â™ªWe shed tearsâ™ª

50:13.831 --> 50:17.583
â™ªDeep blue seas turn to foamâ™ª

50:17.583 --> 50:21.434
â™ªWe regained freedomâ™ª

50:21.434 --> 50:24.163
â™ªIf you remember meâ™ª

50:24.163 --> 50:27.002
â™ªThen I'm pleasedâ™ª

50:40.096 --> 50:44.240
â™ªI just wanna take my time tonightâ™ª

50:46.241 --> 50:50.531
â™ªTo do all the things I said I'd tryâ™ª

50:52.256 --> 50:58.112
